{"tid":2030461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮顧問指資金可能大規模撤離香港 企業不希望在沒法治地方投資","createTime":"2020-05-22T18:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T19:10:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1abedbf9e108c7d736a90053774915e3c431c3","tid":2030461,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"白宮顧問指資金可能大規模撤離香港<br />\n23.05.2020 01:24<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮經濟顧問哈塞特評論在香港立國安法，指中方的舉動非常不利中港經濟，美國正研究可能的對策。他表示，北京面臨資金大規模撤離香港的風險，因為企業不希望在基本上嘲笑法治的地方投資或保留資金，香港將不再成為亞洲金融中心，形容付出的代價非常沉重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289550&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289550%26csid%3D261_341&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=c200212d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289550&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a436ef00c368b85a8b6c4ab8da28bca0e87cac69","tid":2030461,"uid":176282,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:22:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒法治地方</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e80846476a731c56b97e8efe2215c817fe55910","tid":2030461,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"今日林鄭先話依法<br />\n反了反了"},{"pid":"61e3bbb18a36c398f7eb17ed9a6fc00a2dabcea8","tid":2030461,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e80846476a731c56b97e8efe2215c817fe55910","tid":2030461,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"今日林鄭先話依法<br />\n反了反了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"依法人治呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a19874ba6bd92d38d186f0c07ad1479f90cb4d1","tid":2030461,"uid":273228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0